@rickert - I'm trying to use this to cross-compile libxml2 to android from Windows.  This is uncovering some issues, I'll send you some PRs for that on GH.  Is there a reason that the CMake minimum version is so low?  Even the LTS releases of Ubuntu are at newer releases.  @nwellnhof would you have any requirements on a minimum version of CMake to support?

